name: Gatorade Sport Drink Berry No Sugar | 600mL
description:
Gatorade No Sugar contains the essential electrolytes to help replace what's lost in sweat and fuel you to perform at your best, all with zero carbs and minimal calories to compliment your nutritional efforts.


You lose a whole lot more than water when you sweat. Losses in fluids and electrolytes can negatively impact performance. During training and exercise, you burn off vital energy needed to continue competing with the best.


Gatorade is the Number 1 sports rehydration drink on the planet scientifically formulated to help refuel to support the demands you put on your body, which is why it's trusted by some of the world's best athletes. Gatorade No Sugar is no different.


Available in a convenient 600mL sports drink bottle to help replenish and hydrate your body on-the-go.


NOTHING BEATS GATORADE.
Essential Electrolytes

Without the Sugar

name: Maximus Game On Lime Isotonic Sports Drink | 1L
description:
Whether you're trying to stay hydrated at work, attempting to keep cool on a scorching hot day or looking for rapid rehydration after a long game of backyard cricket, our sports drinks are the perfect thirst-quencher for any occasion. Try our great tasting lime flavour that's so good it's almost unfair - with just the right balance of sweetness and refreshment, you'll feel rehydrated.

 

Each bottle contains four key electrolytes - sodium, potassium, magnesium, and calcium - to refuel and rehydrate faster for repaid rehydration, no matter how intense your day (or night was!). With added B Vitamins and Magnesium to reduce tiredness & fatigue.

 

So next time you're feeling parched in the morning on the move or after physical activity, grab a Maximus - the ultimate hydration companion for Aussies.

 

Maximus is available in a large 1L bottle perfect for keeping you replenished for longer, no matter where you are.

 

MORE DRINK, MORE DO.
Isotonic Sports Drink

Essential electrolytes for rapid re-hydration

B Vitamins and Magnesium to reduce tiredness & fatigue

Great taste

Large multi-serve 1L bottle

Recovery.

Lime flavour.
